Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Head MRI
When I select 'Vertigo' from 'Previous interventions/therapies' dropdown menu
Then 'Add clinic' button is enabled
And 'Non-specific vertigo' radio button is enabled
And 'Rotary vertigo' radio button is enabled
And 'Staggering vertigo' radio button is enabled
And 'Chronic' radio button is enabled
And 'Positional vertigo' radio button is enabled
And 'Central vertigo' radio button is enabled
